## 4. Custom Exceptions & Enums

### Enums
*   **`ZonaPesca`**: Defines valid geographical areas for fishing.
    *   *Values:* `YUCATAN`, `CAMPECHE`, `QUINTANA_ROO`, `GOLFO_DE_MEXICO`.
    *   *Feature:* Includes custom Jackson serialization/deserialization for human-readable names.

### Custom Exceptions
*   **`PezNotFoundException`**: Triggered when a fish search by ID or Zone yields no results.
*   **`PezNameNotFoundException`**: Specifically for name-based search failures.
*   **`GlobalExceptionHandler`**: A central component using `@RestControllerAdvice` to map these exceptions to standard HTTP error codes (e.g., 404 Not Found) with detailed error bodies.
